    <title>HEXO FROM THE BEGINNING</title>
    <link href="/2025/12/02/Hexo-How/"/>
    <url>/2025/12/02/Hexo-How/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Initialize-a-Hexo-site"><a href="#Initialize-a-Hexo-site" class="headerlink" title="Initialize a Hexo site"></a>Initialize a Hexo site</h2><ol><li>Check node.js</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">node -v<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>Check git</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git --version<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>Install hexo-cli</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install -g hexo-cli<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="4"><li>Inisitalize a Hexo site</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo init &lt;folder&gt; <br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt; <span class="hljs-comment"># 进入博客目录</span><br>npm install <span class="hljs-comment"># 安装依赖（相当于安装装修材料）</span><br>hexo server        <span class="hljs-comment"># 启动本地预览服务器</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Use-Themes"><a href="#Use-Themes" class="headerlink" title="Use Themes"></a>Use Themes</h3><ol start="5"><li>Use Themes</li></ol><ul><li>安装必要的渲染插件</li><li>git clone 主题仓库到 themes 目录</li><li>在博客目录下编辑 _config.yml 文件，将 theme 字段设置为你选择的主题名称</li></ul><ol start="6"><li>Clean and Start Server</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo clean   <span class="hljs-comment"># 清理缓存（也就是清理 public 文件夹和 db.json）</span><br>hexo g       <span class="hljs-comment"># 重新生成静态文件 (Generate)</span><br>hexo s       <span class="hljs-comment"># 启动服务器 (Server)</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Deploy-to-GitHub-Pages"><a href="#Deploy-to-GitHub-Pages" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to GitHub Pages"></a>Deploy to GitHub Pages</h3><ul><li>在博客目录下编辑 _config.yml 文件，将 deploy 字段设置为如下内容：</li></ul><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">deploy:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">repo:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://github.com/你的用户名/你的用户名.github.io.git</span>  <span class="hljs-string">&lt;--</span> <span class="hljs-string">粘贴刚才复制的地址</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">branch:</span> <span class="hljs-string">main</span>  <span class="hljs-string">&lt;--</span> <span class="hljs-string">注意：现在新仓库默认叫</span> <span class="hljs-string">main，如果是很老的仓库可能叫</span> <span class="hljs-string">master，去</span> <span class="hljs-string">GitHub</span> <span class="hljs-string">确认一下分支名</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>执行部署命令</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<br>hexo g -d      <span class="hljs-comment"># 部署到 GitHub Pages (Deploy)</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>推送代码部分</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git init <span class="hljs-comment">#初始化仓库</span><br>git checkout -b hexo  <span class="hljs-comment"># 创建并切换到 hexo 分支</span><br><br>git add .  <br>git commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Deploy Hexo site to GitHub Pages&quot;</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 提交代码</span><br>git remote add origin https://github.com/你的用户名/你的用户名.github.io.git <br>git push -u origin hexo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>Update blog for reader</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 创建新文章</span><br>hexo g -d      <span class="hljs-comment"># 部署到 GitHub Pages (Deploy)</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>推送代码部分</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git add .  <br>git commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Update My New Post&quot;</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 提交代码</span><br>git push origin hexo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="New-page"><a href="#New-page" class="headerlink" title="New page"></a>New page</h2><ul><li>创建新页面</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo new  <span class="hljs-string">&quot;about&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
